[assistant]   "agent_guidance": "For tests that need devtools/restart to be enabled, account for Spring Boot's DevToolsEnablementDeducer: it returns disabled when the stack contains JUnit/Spring Boot test classes and in native image. Exercise enabled restart/autoconfiguration behavior from a helper thread without a JUnit stack, or for RestartApplicationListener-specific behavior set the system property spring.devtools.restart.enabled=true only around that test and restore it afterward. Do not expect devtools-enabled behavior in native-image runs; keep native assertions to APIs that work with devtools disabled. If remote devtools server/client behavior is tested, set a non-empty spring.devtools.remote.secret test property because remote support is opt-in.",
